# Tera Template Syntax Guide

## Variable Substitution

```tera
{{ variable_name }}
```

## Filters

```tera
{{ variable_name | filter_name }}
{{ name | snake_case }}
{{ text | upper }}
```

## Conditionals

```tera
{% if condition %}
  Content if true
{% else %}
  Content if false
{% endif %}
```

## Loops

```tera
{% for item in array %}
  {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
```

### Loop Variables

- `loop.index` - 1-based index
- `loop.index0` - 0-based index
- `loop.first` - True if first iteration
- `loop.last` - True if last iteration
- `loop.length` - Total items

## Comments

```tera
{# This comment won't appear in output #}
```

## Advanced Features

### Set Variables

```tera
{% set my_var = some_value %}
{{ my_var }}
```

### Include Templates

```tera
{% include "other_template.tera" %}
```

### Inheritance

```tera
{% extends "base.tera" %}

{% block content %}
  Custom content
{% endblock %}
```
